#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:19
msgid ""
"An animation player is used for general-purpose playback of "
":ref:`Animation <class_Animation>` resources. It contains a dictionary of"
" animations (referenced by name) and custom blend times between their "
"transitions. Additionally, animations can be played and blended in "
"different channels."
msgstr ""
"动画播放器用于 :ref:`Animation <class_Animation>` "
"资源的通用播放。它包含一个动画字典（按名称引用）和它们的过渡之间的自定义混合时间。此外，可以在不同的通道中播放和混合动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:21
msgid ""
"``AnimationPlayer`` is more suited than :ref:`Tween <class_Tween>` for "
"animations where you know the final values in advance. For example, "
"fading a screen in and out is more easily done with an "
"``AnimationPlayer`` node thanks to the animation tools provided by the "
"editor. That particular example can also be implemented with a "
":ref:`Tween <class_Tween>` node, but it requires doing everything by "
"code."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:23
msgid "Updating the target properties of animations occurs at process time."
msgstr "在处理时，更新动画的目标属性。"

