msgid "Enumerations"
msgstr "枚举"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:152
msgid "enum **AnimationProcessMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **AnimationProcessMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:154
msgid ""
"**ANIMATION_PROCESS_PHYSICS** = **0** --- Process animation during the "
"physics process. This is especially useful when animating physics bodies."
msgstr "**ANIMATION_PROCESS_PHYSICS** = **0** —— 在物理处理中处理动画。在动画化物理物体时，这特别有用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:156
msgid ""
"**ANIMATION_PROCESS_IDLE** = **1** --- Process animation during the idle "
"process."
msgstr "**ANIMATION_PROCESS_IDLE** = **1** —— 在空闲处理中处理动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:158
msgid ""
"**ANIMATION_PROCESS_MANUAL** = **2** --- Do not process animation. Use "
":ref:`advance <class_AnimationPlayer_method_advance>` to process the "
"animation manually."
msgstr ""
"**ANIMATION_PROCESS_MANUAL** = **2** —— 不处理动画。使用 :ref:`advance "
"<class_AnimationPlayer_method_advance>` 手动处理动画。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:168
msgid "enum **AnimationMethodCallMode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **AnimationMethodCallMode**："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:170
msgid ""
"**ANIMATION_METHOD_CALL_DEFERRED** = **0** --- Batch method calls during "
"the animation process, then do the calls after events are processed. This"
" avoids bugs involving deleting nodes or modifying the AnimationPlayer "
"while playing."
msgstr ""
"**ANIMATION_METHOD_CALL_DEFERRED** = **0** —— "
"在动画过程中进行批量方法调用，然后在事件处理后处理调用。这样可以避免在播放时，涉及删除节点或修改 ``AnimationPlayer`` 的错误。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:172
msgid ""
"**ANIMATION_METHOD_CALL_IMMEDIATE** = **1** --- Make method calls "
"immediately when reached in the animation."
msgstr "**ANIMATION_METHOD_CALL_IMMEDIATE** = **1** —— 在动画中到达时，立即进行方法调用。"

