msgid ""
"Plays the animation with key ``name``. Custom blend times and speed can "
"be set. If ``custom_speed`` is negative and ``from_end`` is ``true``, the"
" animation will play backwards (which is equivalent to calling "
":ref:`play_backwards <class_AnimationPlayer_method_play_backwards>`)."
msgstr ""
"用 ``名称（name）`` 键播放动画。可以设置自定义速度和混合时间。如果 ``custom_speed`` 为负，``from_end`` 为"
" ``true``，则动画将倒放。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:460
msgid ""
"The ``AnimationPlayer`` keeps track of its current or last played "
"animation with :ref:`assigned_animation "
"<class_AnimationPlayer_property_assigned_animation>`. If this method is "
"called with that same animation ``name``, or with no ``name`` parameter, "
"the assigned animation will resume playing if it was paused, or restart "
"if it was stopped (see :ref:`stop <class_AnimationPlayer_method_stop>` "
"for both pause and stop). If the animation was already playing, it will "
"keep playing."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:462
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Note:** The animation will be updated the next time the "
"``AnimationPlayer`` is processed. If other variables are updated at the "
"same time this is called, they may be updated too early. To perform the "
"update immediately, call ``advance(0)``."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：动画将在下次处理 ``AnimationPlayer`` "
"时进行更新。如果被调用时，其他变量同时被更新，则它们可能更新得太早。要立即执行更新，请调用 ``advance(0)``。"

