#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationplayer.rst:506
msgid ""
"Seeks the animation to the ``seconds`` point in time (in seconds). If "
"``update`` is ``true``, the animation updates too, otherwise it updates "
"at process time. Events between the current frame and ``seconds`` are "
"skipped."
msgstr ""
"将动画寻找到 ``seconds`` 处的时间点（以秒为单位）。如果 ``update`` 为 "
"``true``，则动画也会更新，否则会在处理时更新。当前帧和 ``seconds`` 之间的事件将被跳过。"

